%AF%B7%E6%B1%82%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95"><span class="toc-number">1.5.3.</span> <span class="toc-text">HTTP请求方法</span></a><ol class="toc-child"><li class="toc-item toc-level-5"><a class="toc-link" href="#GET"><span class="toc-number">1.5.3.1.</span> <span class="toc-text">GET</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-5"><a class="toc-link" href="#HEAD"><span class="toc-number">1.5.3.2.</span> <span class="toc-text">HEAD</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-5"><a class="toc-link" href="#POST"><span class="toc-number">1.5.3.3.</span> <span class="toc-text">POST</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-5"><a class="toc-link" href="#PUT"><span class="toc-number">1.5.3.4.</span> <span class="toc-text">PUT</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-5"><a class="toc-link" href="#DELETE"><span class="toc-number">1.5.3.5.</span> <span class="toc-text">DELETE</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-5"><a class="toc-link" href="#TRACE"><span class="toc-number">1.5.3.6.</span> <span class="toc-text">TRACE</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-5"><a class="toc-link" href="#OPTIONS"><span class="toc-number">1.5.3.7.</span> <span class="toc-text">OPTIONS</span></a></li></ol></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-4"><a class="toc-link" href="#HTTP%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E8%AF%B7%E6%B1%82%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F-get%E4%B8%8Epost%E8%AF%B7%E6%B1%82%E7%9A%84%E5%8C%BA%E5%88%AB"><span class="toc-number">1.5.4.</span> <span class="toc-text">HTTP常用请求方式: get与post请求的区别</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-4"><a class="toc-link" href="#HTTP%E8%AF%B7%E6%B1%82%E6%A0%BC%E5%BC%8F-%E8%AF%B7%E6%B1%82%E5%8D%8F%E8%AE%AE"><span class="toc-number">1.5.5.</span> <span class="toc-text">HTTP请求格式(请求协议)</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-4"><a class="toc-link" href="#HTTP%E5%93%8D%E5%BA%94%E6%A0%BC%E5%BC%8F%EF%BC%88%E5%93%8D%E5%BA%94%E5%8D%8F%E8%AE%AE%EF%BC%89"><span class="toc-number">1.5.6.</span> <span class="toc-text">HTTP响应格式（响应协议）</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-4"><a class="toc-link" href="#HTTP%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E7%9A%84%E7%8A%B6%E6%80%81%E7%A0%81"><span class="toc-number">1.5.7.</span> <span class="toc-text">HTTP常见的状态码</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-4"><a class="toc-link" href="#HTTPS%E5%8D%8F%E8%AE%AE"><span class="toc-number">1.5.8.</span> <span class="toc-text">HTTPS协议</span></a></li></ol></li></ol></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E7%88%AC%E8%99%AB%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89"><span class="toc-number">2.</span> <span class="toc-text">网络爬虫的定义</span></a><ol class="toc-child"><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E7%88%AC%E8%99%AB%E7%9A%84%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB"><span class="toc-number">2.1.</span> <span class="toc-text">爬虫的分类</span></a><ol class="toc-child"><li class="toc-item toc-level-4"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E9%80%9A%E7%94%A8%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E7%88%AC%E8%99%AB"><span class="toc-number">2.1.1.</span> <span class="toc-text">通用网络爬虫</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-4"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E8%81%9A%E7%84%A6%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E7%88%AC%E8%99%AB"><span class="toc-number">2.1.2.</span> <span class="toc-text">聚焦网络爬虫</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-4"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E5%A2%9E%E9%87%8F%E5%BC%8F%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E7%88%AC%E8%99%AB"><span class="toc-number">2.1.3.</span> <span class="toc-text">增量式网络爬虫</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-4"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E6%B7%B1%E5%B1%82%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E7%88%AC"><span class="toc-number">2.1.4.</span> <span class="toc-text">深层网络爬</span></a></li></ol></li></ol></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E7%88%AC%E8%99%AB%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%AD%A5%E9%AA%A4"><span class="toc-number">3.</span> <span class="toc-text">爬虫的基本步骤</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E7%88%AC%E8%99%AB%E6%B6%89%E5%8F%8A%E7%9A%84-Python-%E6%A8%A1%E5%9D%97"><span class="toc-number">4.</span> <span clas